<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.1.11">
<l>viyappāya viyappillā meyñāṉa vētiyaṉaic</l>
<l>cayappukaḻār palarvāḻun taṭaṅkurukūrc caṭakōpaṉ</l>
<l>ṟuyakkiṉṟu toḻuturaitta vāyirattu ḷippattu</l>
<l>muyakkoṇṭu piṟappaṟukku molimunnīr ñālattē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>These ten among the thousand that were composed, worshipping without fatigue,</l>
<l>by Caṭakōpaṉ of Kurukūr with tanks where many live that are amply full of praise</l>
<l>on the Vedic one with true knowledge who is a wonder, who is without wonder,</l>
<l>will cut off [re]birth, taking to liberation, in the world [surrounded by] the roaring three-watered [sea].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
